  <h4>Whose Life Will Your Donation Transform?</h4>
  <div class="thumbmail-wrap">
    <img src="/_images/home/1-arzell.jpg" width="319" height="235" alt="Donated goods to The Salvation Army goes toward our rehabilitation centers to save men suffering from addiction and poverty. Purchased goods from our Family Thrift Stores help fund rehabilitation for men and women in need.">
